Package cs.ualberta.ca.medlog.entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BodyLocation
    Description:
    Class representing a record's body location in the application.
    EncryptedPhoto
    Description:
    Class for holding the string representation of an encrypted photo used in storage on the Elastic Search Server.
    MapLocation
    Description:
    Class representing a record's map location in the application.
    Photo
    Description:
    The purpose of this class is to hold a representation of a photo in terms of its path in the files and potentially a bitmap that can be grabbed again.
    Problem
    Description:
    This class represents a patient's problem in the application, this problem possesses an id, title, date, description and records.
    Record
    Description:
    This class represents a problem's record in the application, records possess a id, creator username and timestamp.
    SearchResult
    Description:
    This class represents the information required for producing search results for patients and care providers.
